  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study in a real-world community was designed to perform epidemiological
      investigation and assess effect of CPAP intervention of obstructive sleep apnea.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with obstructive sleep apnea receiving CPAP or not would be observed in years.
      Primarily Impact of CPAP on health assessment andx control rate of hypertension would
      evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
